00:54.270 --> 00:55.520 line:90%
Hi!

00:55.520 --> 00:57.470 line:90%
I'm Jenny.

00:57.470 --> 00:59.130 line:90%
Nice to meet you.

01:00.720 --> 01:02.180 line:90%
